      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source of parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including rust and large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functioning electronics. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul and the transmission is currently slipping, meaning it is not in drivable condition and will need to be towed. While it was once a reliable model, it has not been maintained in recent years and requires substantial investment to return to the road.",
