    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presented in superlative condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade specimen of unrivaled preservation. Every attribute, from the factory-original finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous climate-controlled storage and exacting maintenance. This is a showroom-quality masterpiece intended for the collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
