    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman in Guards Red. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, protected by a professional ceramic coating with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the black leather interior remains taut and pristine, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; the bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and every switchgear functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively through authorized Porsche centers. With exceptionally low mileage and a fully documented pedigree, this is a true investment-grade example that will satisfy the most discerning enthusiast. No modifications, no track time, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
